a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: A modern take on our renowned SCF chorus pedal and including a sweet Tri-Chorus setting, Corona Chorus combines a blast from the past with superbly shimmering sounds and features.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Corona Chorus

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: Flashback 2 Delay brings expression pedal performance to the legendary Flashback Delay and more. New Crystal preset adds a shimmer to your playing and realistic Tape and Analog algorithms lets you sound better than ever.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Flashback 2 Delay

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: Flashback Delay is a modern twist on the know-how and legacy of TC Electronic's legendary 2290 delay, featuring 7 seconds of delay and every delay type known to mankind.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Flashback Delay

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: Flashback X4 Delay is so much more than the sum of four Flashback pedals. You'll get 15 delay types, Three presets, Tap Tempo, TonePrint a looper and more.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Flashback X4 Delay

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: Hall Of Fame 2 Reverb takes up where its predecessor left off. Along with doing everything the original Hall Of Fame did, you also get MASH technology for limitless expression, Shimmer, and 3 TonePrint slots. This pedal represents a new way to reverb.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Hall of Fame 2 Reverb

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: Reverb is very much about space. But then again, so is your pedal board. So what if we could combine unlimited space for your reverbs with a miniature footprint? What? You’d be partying on for days? Well, break out the confetti, cos it’s here!
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Hall of Fame Mini Reverb

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: Hall Of Fame allows you to experiment and play with reverb the way you see fit. With 10 different reverb types from plates to springs to churches and back, you'll never be without a great reverb sound the way you imagine it.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Hall of Fame Reverb

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: Helix Phaser is the most versatile phaser pedal ever made. It delivers both smooth vintage phaser tones and lush modern sounds straight out of the box, while TonePrint pushes this pedal into creative overdrive, letting you create your own phaser tones from scratch.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Helix Phaser

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: Pipeline Tap Tremolo is the most versatile tremolo pedal ever, featuring quality tremolo tones in vintage and square modes along with TonePrint for a totally customizable tremolo sound. Add to that a tap tempo footswitch and a volume boost in a small enclosure and you’ve got a tidal wave of cool tremolo coming at you.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Pipeline Tap Tremolo

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: vibrato is what makes playing come alive. And from a subtle warble to Leslie sounds, Shaker Vibrato does what it can to liven things up! You'l get 2 vibrato types, Great controls, including 'Rise-Time' and Latch-mode
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Shaker Vibrato

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: SpectraComp Bass Compressor is the tiniest big thing to hit the world of bass in a long time. This ultra-compact and highly intuitive multiband compressor, is made to bring out all of the glorious low-end punch and presence of your beloved bass in the most transparent and musical way you've ever heard. Just turn it on and take charge of the groove.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: SpectraComp Bass Compressor

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: Sub 'N' Up Mini Octaver is the little leader of the pitch-pack. Featuring our next generation octave-engine and individual blend controls for dry, octave-up and octave-down, Sub 'N' Up Mini is set to deliver flawless octave tracking through complex chords and groovy single-note lines. And with the option of adding modulation to the mix via our free TonePrint editor, for organ warble octaves, Sub 'N' Up Mini Octaver is the new authority on tiny pitch manipulation.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Sub 'N' Up Mini Octaver

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: Sub 'N' Up Octaver is the new leader of the pitch-pack. Featuring our superb next generation octave-engine and individual blend controls for dry, octave-up and two sub-octaves, Sub 'N' Up is set to deliver flawless octave tones whether you're playing complex chords or groovy single-note lines. And with the option of adding modulation to the mix via our high-powered TonePrint editor, for spacey ambient octaves, Sub 'N' Up Octaver truly is the definition of pitch perfection.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Sub 'N' Up Octaver

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: The Dreamscape is a John Petrucci Signature Pedal that houses Chorus, Flanger and Vibrato effects that will keep you challenged, inspired and coming round for riff-inspiring possibilities.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: The Dreamscape

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: A dead on digital recreation of the legendary Shin-Ei Uni-Vibe. Viscous Vibe brings all the drippy swirls and gooey goodness on tap, echoing the original unit to a tee. Now add TonePrint to the equation and you have every classic rock players new dream pedal.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Viscous Vibe

a:CmsProductFull.a:Description: The Vortex Flanger is an amazing sounding Flange with some added tricks up its sleeve - allowing it to follow you from a subtle 70s woosh through a more Eddie-type vibe to a twisted soundscape of futuristic fantasticness.
a:CmsProductFull.a:Name: Vortex Flanger
